pageProduct.name: Wanderlust Plant Iron 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Vegan source of iron derived from Curry Leaf to relieve tiredness and support red blood cell health.

Wanderlust Plant Iron is a consciously created vegan source of iron derived from Curry Leaf to relieve tiredness and fatigue, support transport of oxygen in the body and maintain red blood cell health. Vitamin C derived from Amla assists with the absorption of dietary iron.

Size: 60 Capsules

Warnings

Contains Sulfites.

Not for the treatment of iron deficiency conditions.

If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Vitamin and mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:

Murraya koenigii (Organic Curry Leaf) leaf ext. dry conc. stand. 333.33 mg
Derived from min. dry 16.67 g
Equiv. iron 12 mg
Phyllanthus emblica (Organic Amla) fruit ext. dry conc. 30 mg
Derived from dry 1.2 g
Equiv. ascorbic acid (Vitamin C) 6 mg

No added gluten, dairy, lactose, soy, egg, artificial colours or artificial flavours. Suitable for vegetarians and vegans.

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Take two capsules daily or as directed by your healthcare practitioner.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry
place. Do not use if cap seal or
inner seal is missing or broken.
